                     <h3>Dimebag Darrel:</h3>
                     <img src="https://e1.pxfuel.com/desktop-wallpaper/303/323/desktop-wallpaper-dimebag-darrell-dimebag-darrel-thumbnail.jpg"
                     alt="Dimebag" width="200" height="350"> <br>
                     <strong>Dimebag Darrel Lance Abbot</strong> (August 20, 1966- December 8,2004).
                     The lead guitarist of the Thrash Metal band <mark>Pantera.</mark>
                     Every guitarist will admit that all the compositions of Dimebag 
                     are the  most toughest riffs. Also frankly till today after him, no one really
                     played the Pantera songs the way Dimebag played cos his playing was quite impossible
                     and only a guitarist with good practice can only play like him. The death of Dimebag was really
                     tragic for the metal scene.Pantera has realeasd 21 albums and <strong>the top 5 albums are: </strong> <br>
                     <br>
