            <h3>Dave Mustaine:</h3> <br>
            <img src="https://townsquare.media/site/366/files/2022/03/attachment-megadeth_dave_mustaine_1988.jpg?w=780&q=75" alt="Dave Mustaine"
            width="350" >
            <br>
            <strong>David Scott Mustaine</strong> (Born 1961 September 13,1961)
            is the Vocal and the guitarist of the thrash metal band <mark>Megadeth.</mark>
The speciality of Mustaine is his background music in Megadeth.
His complicated riffs (mostly in 150-182 bpm) made the songs more heavy and creative.
There always have been a competition between the heavy metal band <strong>Metallica</strong>
and Megadeth about their albums. In my opinion megadeth and metallica can't be compared
because megadeth's song is more different and "heavier" and Metallica is also heavy with a little
bit of "beauty". The <strong> top 5 albums of Megadeth</strong> are: <br>
