                                    <h3>John Petrucci:</h3>
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/16/86/01/1686013cd72894632197c23fe52f75a7.jpg" alt="John Petrucci"
                                    width="200" height="300"> 
                                    <br>
                                    <strong>John Petrucci</strong> (Born July 12, 1967)
                                    is the lead guitarist of the prog metal band <mark>Dream Theater.</mark>
                                    Whatever I say about this guy is less because he's just amazing. The beauty of Dream theater is their extremly 
                                    complicated odd time signatures in their songs (most of them are nearly an half hour)
                                    and if you want to learn their songs..... you want to kill yourself- <br>
                                    John Petrucci has also influenced a lots of musicians who are at the peak of their success now.
                                    Every albums of Dream Theater is extremly magical but if I still have to mention some they are:<br>
